    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crafting</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/8b371f01ac137f13f4b424b40d56689d.poster.avif?t=1741743002\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/8b371f01ac137f13f4b424b40d56689d.webm?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/8b371f01ac137f13f4b424b40d56689d.mp4?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since the dawn of man jars have been made with 3 core components; The Rim, bastion of creation simple yet elegant. The Lid, an unstoppable force exuding a constant pressure onto the rim. The Glass, the very <i>soul </i> of the jar. Together with your assistant Hanna you can order a variety of resources to craft your own customizable jars!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique customers</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/febcd391e981ad269d76664ea269198e.poster.avif?t=1741743002\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/febcd391e981ad269d76664ea269198e.webm?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/febcd391e981ad269d76664ea269198e.mp4?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a cast of 100s of unique customers with their own preferred styles of jars. Fall in love with a <span class=\"bb_strike\">un</span>forgettable cast of lil guys, and jimbo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishing</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/2adb70cb8a3a210ec4e645ac0d1e4a0b.poster.avif?t=1741743002\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/2adb70cb8a3a210ec4e645ac0d1e4a0b.webm?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/2adb70cb8a3a210ec4e645ac0d1e4a0b.mp4?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your jars to clean up the ocean.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/b30bc34ce57b8df1edf7ea71908845c0.poster.avif?t=1741743002\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/b30bc34ce57b8df1edf7ea71908845c0.webm?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139470/extras/b30bc34ce57b8df1edf7ea71908845c0.mp4?t=1741743002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate the shop with various furnishing customers gift you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
